	   <tr><td colspan=2>"Velious Required" means that you have to&nbsp;&nbsp;have Velious to get the weapon via a drop.  If someone gets this sword to drop in Velious and wants to sell it to someone that doesn't have Velious, they can.  But the latter person's only avenue of obtaining Velious equipment is just that:  buying them from someone who's been over there.  <br><br>Someone probably sold that blade to a vendor in Freeport not long before you bought it from them, I imagine.  That same person could have given the blade to some bat outside the city gates and some lucky newbie could have looted it from that bat if they were to kill it shortly thereafter.  <br>&nbsp;<br>Wayzup Wanderon<br>Hmm...that's strange...no wait, that's ME that's strange...</td></tr>
