	   <tr><td colspan=2>Both Rixact and Smason can drop this.&nbsp;&nbsp;(Names both preceded by Foreman)<br><br>Sells to merchants at indifferent faction for 25 plat.  If you realize how much plat one can make off the stuff in the Giants in Frontier Mountains.... these are common spawns.  Rixact spawns at the very bottom, on a slight outcropping.  It's his little 'Pride Rock' of the Caverns.  Smason is a static spawn, can spawn anywhere a Ry'Gorr WATCHMAN can spawn.  Not where a miner can spawn.  I've hunted here for almost two weeks, and never had him spawn in a miner's spot.<br><br>Foremen drop the Frozen Longsword, and Smason and Rixact can do the same.  I had Smason a couple times with one velium weapon and one frozen longsword.  Horrible, would have died without my cleric, Soot.<br>&nbsp;<br>Menuven Amoray Altruah-Wylt<br>49th Ranger<br>Tribunal</td></tr>
